sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Hook as Traceability Hook
    participant FS as File System
    participant Command

    User->>Hook: /arckit:traceability
    Hook->>FS: Scan & extract (all I/O in Node.js)
    FS-->>Hook: Raw file contents
    Hook->>Hook: Extract requirement IDs
    Hook->>Hook: Compute coverage
    Hook->>Command: Inject tables via additionalContext
    Note over Hook,Command: Zero Read operations<br/>~2,000 tokens (tables only)

    Command->>Command: Build matrix from tables (AI reasoning)
    Command->>Command: Generate report (AI reasoning)
